{"tid":498978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網售自製遊戲機預載千款侵權遊戲　海關拘2人","createTime":"2017-12-14T10:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T11:32:54.000Z","uid":46356,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d20f58fcb52f744bdff2d331368e1d6bea7b34a0","tid":498978,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:07:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171213/bkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171213%2Fbkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001.html&d=VgOsMrzToc1whm0geNSfc4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=c729d05d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171213/bkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n網售自製遊戲機預載千款侵權遊戲　海關拘2人<br />\n<br />\n「將機鋪搬返屋企」、「支援遊戲超過7,000款」，一間智能產品公司今年中推出一款自家品牌家用遊戲機，標榜僅約3吋機身載有逾7,000款懷舊遊戲，包括街機、Game Gear、Game Boy、紅白機等，可直插電視或平板電腦使用，又支援多人對戰。該公司拍攝宣傳片在facebook推銷，連手掣的遊戲機套裝售價949港元，聲稱全球限量1,000部。<br />\n<br />\n該公司為吸引顧客，更提供免費送貨、原廠保養等服務，吸引不少資深玩家購買。惟海關近日接獲舉報，指該款電視遊戲機預載的遊戲懷疑侵犯版權，遂於今日下午採取反盜版執法行動，掩至深水埗福仁商場門市作突擊搜查，起出12部遊戲機套裝，總值約1.1萬港元，將男店主（35歲）及男店員（23歲）拘捕，涉嫌涉及銷售或為售賣用途而管有侵權物品，2人被海關押走調查。<br />\n<br />\n今次是海關首次緝破有店舖以自製遊戲機預載侵權遊戲的案件，初步相信該公司運作約1年，半年前起出售該款侵權產品，遊戲機由內地廠商製造，行動仍然繼續，不排除有更多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該公司總部設於葵興一棟工廈，過往曾推出多款創意智能產品，包括具攝錄功能的遙控「偵探車」、供小朋友學寫字的手寫板、無線投影「手指」、GPS追踪手錶等，其中手錶具備單向監聽、一鍵求救、運動量記錄等功能，吸引不少家長訂購，用於遙距監控子女及防止走失。<br />\n<br />\n海關押走被捕男子。（劉子文攝）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171213/photo/bkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001_02b.jpg?20171214062734\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20171214062734&h=396bc906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲機套裝包括街機手掣。（劉子文攝）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171213/photo/bkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001_03b.jpg?20171214062734\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20171214062734&h=b84eac21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海關檢走多部遊戲機套裝。（劉子文攝）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171213/photo/bkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001_04b.jpg?20171214062734\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20171214062734&h=89569b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n檢獲的多部遊戲機。（劉子文攝）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171213/photo/bkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001_05b.jpg?20171214062734\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001_05b.jpg%3F20171214062734&h=0873fe71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上宣傳片標榜毋須下載安裝，即插即玩。（互聯網）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171213/photo/bkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001_06b.jpg?20171214062734\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20171214062734&h=506d5759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲機支援超過7,000款遊戲。（互聯網）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171213/photo/bkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001_07b.jpg?20171214062734\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001_07b.jpg%3F20171214062734&h=d148327e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲機可插電視或平板電腦玩。（互聯網）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171213/photo/bkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001_08b.jpg?20171214062734\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171213210914209-1213_00822_001_08b.jpg%3F20171214062734&h=325d39b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\